{"tid":1141822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商場內偷走兩件衣服 警員涉高買今提堂","createTime":"2019-05-06T17:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T00:50:44.000Z","uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfddcad901843224d48be97296e463683df309ed","tid":1141822,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"觀塘道418號創紀之城，昨午1時許，一名50歲姓劉休班警員，涉嫌在一間店舖內偷走兩件總值約128元衣服，29歲姓張職員發現報警，警員到場調查調查劉拒絕合作，稍後被警員拘捕帶署扣查，劉被暫控一項盜竊罪及一項阻礙警務人員執行職務罪，案件將於明日於觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n免責聲明：<br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">投資涉及風險，證券價格有時會大幅波動，價格可升亦可跌，更可變 得毫無價值。 投資未必一定能夠賺取利潤，反而可能會招致損失，往績數字並非 未來表現的指標。</span></del><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd2094f2fd205770448a8e85a31e1e7cfeabd91b","tid":1141822,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"128蚊都要偷<br />\n乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f6ea7d111d998ebe5aa28a362c45c856f6dd85","tid":1141822,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"高層又震怒"},{"pid":"623e5965d5df4522c69cdb2212de101dd7378325","tid":1141822,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:29:42.000Z","msg":"班差佬係咪弱智"},{"pid":"de358744d2dc1f91d984558d44ab9a4424983e43","tid":1141822,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24f6ea7d111d998ebe5aa28a362c45c856f6dd85","tid":1141822,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"高層又震怒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"柏金遜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f338852fc51e1491dd9359616b87f356b4f2c6a6","tid":1141822,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"休班警員阻礙警務人員執行職務<img src=